%% Evidence: APS-E004, APS-E002, APS-E001, APS-E003
sequenceDiagram
  participant User
  participant Login as LoginClient
  participant Auth as Auth.js credentials
  participant DB as Prisma User
  participant Session as JWT session

  User->>Login: Submit email/password
  Login->>Login: Clear stale session if present
  Login->>Auth: signIn credentials with optional Turnstile token
  Auth->>Auth: Validate schema and rate limits
  Auth->>Auth: Verify Turnstile
  Auth->>DB: Fetch minimal user fields
  DB-->>Auth: User with password hash and flags
  Auth->>Auth: bcrypt compare
  Auth->>Session: Seed token fields and authTime
  Session-->>Login: Sign-in result
  Login-->>User: Redirect to safe callback or home
